<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, April 16 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan Kenneth Cheruiyot pulled
away in the last kilometers to win the 20th Rotterdam Marathon
Sunday in two hours eight minutes and 22 seconds, according to
reports reaching here.
</P>
<P>
