semi-autonomous Zanzibar region where police officers were beaten
up and their firearms stolen by mobs, the premier said this will
not be entertained any more.
</P>
<P>
The Isles region off mainland Tanzania is the base of Civic
United Front, Tanzania's largest opposition party.
</P>
<P>
He said during the countdown of the multiparty general
elections to be held this October, irate political leaders are
trying to secure popularity and support through different means.
</P>
<P>
