countries, it will be groundless to discuss the contribution of
international trade to the development and poverty reduction,"
said Xiao Gang, deputy governor of the People's Bank of China, at
the 63rd meeting of the Ministers of the Intergovernmental Group
of Twenty-Four (G-24) on International Monetary Affairs. (G-24-
China)
