Blair, who met Putin last month before his election at a high-
profile encounter in St Petersburg, made clear that he intended to
take the Russian leader to task over alleged human rights excesses
in Chechnya.
</P>
<P>
Putin, who flew in from the former Soviet state of Belarus,is
due to leave Britain late on Monday. 
